title: Penny Longboard - Beach Cruising
description:
The new 36” Penny Longboard offers the ultimate way to escape the daily grind and is now available in six classic colour combinations. 

We’ve created a brand new secret plastic formula for added strength and flex control, to ensure this longboard rides like nothing else. You’ll have endless fun cruising around on the longest ever Penny Skateboard.
